228inline bool operator==( QwtEventPattern::MousePattern b1,
229 QwtEventPattern::MousePattern b2 )
230{
231 return b1.button == b2.button && b1.modifiers == b2.modifiers;

235inline bool operator==( QwtEventPattern::KeyPattern b1,
